high_descs: Walk straight to the stove, turn right when you reach the stove, turn right to face the table.
Pick up the knife sitting on the table.
Turn right, walk straight to the counter, and turn right to face the stove.
Place the knife inside the pan sitting on the stove.
Pick up the pan with the knife in it.
Turn left to face the counter, turn left again, walk straight, and turn left to face the table.
Place the pan with the knife in it on the table.
anns.task_desc: Place a pan with a knife in it on the table.

high_descs: Move forward toward the store, then turn right, move forward then turn right again to face the table.
Pick up the knife from the table, in front of the sponge.
Turn right, move forward, then turn right again to face the stove.
Put the knife inside of the pot on the right of the stove.
Pick up the pot with the knife in it.
Turn around, go straight, then turn left to face the table.
Place the pot on the table, to the right of the wine.
anns.task_desc: Put a pot with a knife in it on the table.

high_descs: Walk towards the stove, turn right, take a step, and then turn right to face the green table.
Pick up the yellow knife to the left of the pencil on the table.
Turn around and head towards the stove.
Place the knife in the right square pan.
Pick up the pan from the stove.
Turn around, take a step towards, and face the green table on your left.
Place the pan to the right of the wine bottle on the table.
anns.task_desc: Place a pan with the knife on the green table.

high_descs: Walk to the oven then turn right and walk to the edge of the green table.
Pick up the yellow knife to the left of the blue pencil.
Turn right and walk to the stove.
Place the knife in the pot on the right of the stove.
Pick up the pot on the right of the stove.
Turn around and walk to the middle of the green table.
Place the pot in front of the glass vase on the table.
anns.task_desc: Place a pot with a yellow knife in it in front of the glass vase on the green table.
